                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def16-853-18500408 t18500408-853-punishment-149"></join>
                     <hi rend="italic">To enter into their own recognizances, to appear and receive judgment when called upon, and to keep the peace for one year.</hi>
                  </rs>
               </p>
